node.text:
Here is my vision of the ocean and what I’ve been capturing for the last 10 years in Tahiti. 
The beauty of the underwater world and the crystal clear water from Tahiti are fascinating !
See more of this world in my book SURFACE available on my website. (Link in bio)
Music : BEAT ME 1 by Jonatan Jarpehag
